### Test des endpoints SSE

# Variables d'environnement
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Test SSE Events Stream
GET {{baseUrl}}/github/events/stream?token={{token}}
Accept: text/event-stream
Cache-Control: no-cache

### 2. Test SSE Posts Stats Stream
GET {{baseUrl}}/github/posts/stats/stream?token={{token}}
Accept: text/event-stream
Cache-Control: no-cache

### 3. Test SSE Quota Stream
GET {{baseUrl}}/quota/stream?token={{token}}
Accept: text/event-stream
Cache-Control: no-cache

### 4. Test SSE Events Count Stream (existant)
GET {{baseUrl}}/github/events/length/stream?token={{token}}
Accept: text/event-stream
Cache-Control: no-cache

### 5. Test CORS Options pour Events Stream
OPTIONS {{baseUrl}}/github/events/stream
Access-Control-Request-Method: GET
Access-Control-Request-Headers: Cache-Control, Last-Event-ID
Origin: http://localhost:3000

### 6. Test CORS Options pour Posts Stats Stream
OPTIONS {{baseUrl}}/github/posts/stats/stream
Access-Control-Request-Method: GET
Access-Control-Request-Headers: Cache-Control, Last-Event-ID
Origin: http://localhost:3000

### 7. Test CORS Options pour Quota Stream
OPTIONS {{baseUrl}}/quota/stream
Access-Control-Request-Method: GET
Access-Control-Request-Headers: Cache-Control, Last-Event-ID
Origin: http://localhost:3000

### Instructions d'utilisation :

# 1. Remplacez YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE par un token JWT valide
# 2. Démarrez l'API avec : npm run start:dev
# 3. Testez les endpoints un par un
# 4. Vérifiez que vous recevez des événements SSE

# Format attendu des réponses SSE :
# data: {"type":"events","events":[...]}
# data: {"type":"stats","stats":{"drafts":5,"ready":2,...}}
# data: {"type":"quota","quota":{"used":3,"remaining":2}}